      <div class="terms terms-inline">Posted in: <ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_166 first"><a href="/taxonomy/term/166" rel="tag" title="">Legalization</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_151"><a href="/taxonomy/term/151" rel="tag" title="">Marijuana Policy</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_98 last"><a href="/taxonomy/term/98" rel="tag" title="">Press Release</a></li>
